window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Violet</b><br>I've always known that loving Dominic Blackwell comes with risks, but the danger has never felt as real as it does now. We’ve faced so much together, and even though the shadows of his world loom large, I can’t imagine my life without him. I’m ready to fight for our future, no matter what it takes.</p><p><b>Dominic</b><br>My past has always been dark, but Violet has brought light into my life. She’s the only thing that keeps me grounded, and I’ll do whatever it takes to protect her. But the dangers we face are relentless, and I’m willing to sacrifice everything to keep her safe—even if it means confronting my deepest fears.</p>"; 
